     <h1>The Alumni &amp; Parent Relations Office </h1> 
     <p><span style="text-align:justify;">The Alumni &amp; Parent Relations Office acts as the liaison between Westmont and alumni.&nbsp;This office is dedicated to keeping you informed of the latest at Westmont and how you can be involved. Teri, Lorinda, Sergio, and Beth all hope to get to know you and are available to serve you.</span></p> 
     <p><br> <img src="images/TeriBradfordRouse_11.11.jpg" width="210" height="315" alt="Teri Bradford Rouse"> <br> <br> </p> 
     <p>&nbsp;</p> 
