     <p class="txt_indent_no_space" style="text-align:justify;">&nbsp;</p> 
     <p style="text-align:justify;">The Office of Alumni and Parent Relations is committed to keeping you in touch with the latest news and events at Westmont. We also wish to provide you with various programs and services both on and off campus that allow you to be connected with fellow alumni and with Westmont. Continue to check our Web site for upcoming events and information.</p> 
